{
  "title": "Airflow Observability — V3 Low Cardinality",
  "uid": "airflow-observability-v3",
  "tags": ["airflow", "v3", "low-cardinality", "production"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "5s",
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "dag_id",
        "label": "DAG",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
        "query": "label_values(task_status{job=\"airflow_tasks\"}, dag_id)",
        "sort": 1,
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*",
        "multi": true
      },
      {
        "name": "task_id",
        "label": "Task",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
        "query": "label_values(task_status{job=\"airflow_tasks\", dag_id=~\"$dag_id\"}, task_id)",
        "sort": 1,
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*",
        "multi": true
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 24, "h": 4 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## ✅ V3: Production Low-Cardinality Dashboard\nThis dashboard uses the **V3 Production Plugin**, which removes `run_id` from the grouping key.\n\n**The Trade-off:**\n- ✅ **Bounded Cardinality:** Series count = number of unique tasks. No TSDB bloat.\n- ✅ **Latest State:** Always shows the result of the *most recent* execution.\n- ❌ **No Per-Run Identity:** You cannot distinguish between Run A and Run B here. Use structured logs or OLAP for per-run audit history.\n\n**Enable with:** `AIRFLOW_VAR_ENABLE_V3_LOW_CARDINALITY=true`"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "📊 Latest Fleet Status (Most Recent Run)",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 4, "w": 24, "h": 1 },
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Tasks Currently Failed",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 5, "w": 12, "h": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "count(task_status{job=\"airflow_tasks\", dag_id=~\"$dag_id\", task_id=~\"$task_id\"} == -1) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "Failed",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": { "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }, { "color": "red", "value": 1 }] }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Tasks Currently Succeeded",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 5, "w": 12, "h": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "count(task_status{job=\"airflow_tasks\", dag_id=~\"$dag_id\", task_id=~\"$task_id\"} == 1) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "Succeeded",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": { "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }] }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "📈 Fleet Health Trends (Over Time)",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 11, "w": 24, "h": 1 },
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Active Failures Over Time",
      "description": "Counts how many task series currently hold a value of -1 at each scrape interval.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 12, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "count(task_status{job=\"airflow_tasks\", dag_id=~\"$dag_id\"} == -1) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "Failed Tasks",
          "instant": false
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "red" } } }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Active Successes Over Time",
      "description": "Counts how many task series currently hold a value of 1 at each scrape interval.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 12, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "count(task_status{job=\"airflow_tasks\", dag_id=~\"$dag_id\"} == 1) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "Succeeded Tasks",
          "instant": false
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "green" } } }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "🔍 Fleet Inventory",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 20, "w": 24, "h": 1 },
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Latest Task Status Inventory",
      "description": "Shows the current state of every task in the fleet. 1=success, -1=failed",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 21, "w": 24, "h": 10 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "task_status{job=\"airflow_tasks\", dag_id=~\"$dag_id\", task_id=~\"$task_id\"}",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": { "Time": true, "__name__": true, "instance": true, "job": true },
            "renameByName": { "Value": "Latest Status" }
          }
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": { "displayMode": "color-background" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": -1 },
              { "color": "green", "value": 1 }
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}
